* BMAP phase-8 OPSYN: "NEW OPSYN OLD" aliases NEW to the existing op OLD, so it
* assembles identically.  LOADA->LDA and STOREQ->STQ: the alias and the original
* must produce the same word.
       OUNAME OPSYNT
LOADA  OPSYN  LDA
STOREQ OPSYN  STQ
       LOADA  5
       LDA    5
       STOREQ 10
       STQ    10
       END
